Content-Length: 33
WWW-Authenticate: NTLM TlRMTVNTUAACAAAACAAIADAAAACGgAEAq6U1NAWaJCIAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA4AAAATlRMTUF1dGg=

This is still not the real page!
</data1401>

<data1402>
