# Client-side
<client>
<features>
NTLM
SSL
!SSPI
</features>
<server>
http
</server>
<tool>
libauthretry
</tool>

<name>
HTTP authorization retry (Basic switching to NTLM)
</name>
<command>
http://%HOSTIP:%HTTPPORT/%TESTNUMBER basic ntlm
</command>
</client>

